<subSubSection id="C301F0D2FFB7FF98A3A9FDAFFAE665D4" pageId="4" pageNumber="455" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BA4A359FFB7FF98A3A9FDAFFAE665D4" blockId="4.[151,1437,402,645]" pageId="4" pageNumber="455">
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFB7FF98A3A9FDAFFE9C656C" bold="true" box="[151,256,546,572]" pageId="4" pageNumber="455">Remark.</emphasis>
This species was firstly reported from 
<collectingCountry id="F30CE3C9FFB7FF98A1FDFDAEFCB4656D" box="[707,808,547,573]" name="Morocco" pageId="4" pageNumber="455">Morocco</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8ADEA8FFB7FF98A068FDAFFBF8656C" author="Valladares, L. F. &amp; Diaz, J. A. &amp; Garrido, J. &amp; Sainz-Cantero, C. E. &amp; Delgado, J. A." box="[854,1124,546,572]" pageId="4" pageNumber="455" refId="ref28842" refString="Valladares, L. F., Diaz, J. A., Garrido, J., Sainz-Cantero, C. E. &amp; Delgado, J. A. (2018) Coleoptera Hydraenidae. In: R. Sanchez, M. A. (Ed.), Fauna Iberica. Vol. 44. Museo Nacional de Ciencias Naturales, Madrid, pp. 1 - 516." type="book" year="2018">
Valladares 
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFB7FF98A0EDFDAEFB92656C" box="[979,1038,546,572]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="455">et al.</emphasis>
(2018)
</bibRefCitation>
, but without specifying the locality. The species seems typical of temporary waters and only found during winter or early spring (
<bibRefCitation id="EF8ADEA8FFB7FF98A618FDCBFEDE65D4" author="Valladares, L. F. &amp; Diaz, J. A. &amp; Garrido, J. &amp; Sainz-Cantero, C. E. &amp; Delgado, J. A." pageId="4" pageNumber="455" refId="ref28842" refString="Valladares, L. F., Diaz, J. A., Garrido, J., Sainz-Cantero, C. E. &amp; Delgado, J. A. (2018) Coleoptera Hydraenidae. In: R. Sanchez, M. A. (Ed.), Fauna Iberica. Vol. 44. Museo Nacional de Ciencias Naturales, Madrid, pp. 1 - 516." type="book" year="2018">
Valladares 
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFB7FF98A3F8FDE6FF6265D4" box="[198,254,618,644]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="455">et al.</emphasis>
2018
</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry id="F30CE3C9FFB7FF98A24DFDE6FE4465D5" box="[371,472,619,645]" name="Morocco" pageId="4" pageNumber="455">Morocco</collectingCountry>
it has been found during the middle of spring in slow banks downstream of a dam.
</paragraph>
